Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.37,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}美畜同好会 网站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}今夜又被谁所委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}美畜同好会\n确定进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.02,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}密码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.04,0:00:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}绘里香 我的绘里香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}我们公司的社长秘书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.68,0:01:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}一旦离开工作\n看起来就非常优秀温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.57,0:01:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}太理想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}录像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.08,0:01:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}资料都在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.08,0:01:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}整理的很快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}我觉得你会需要\n所以早上就开始整理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}还有什么别的需要吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.97,0:01:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}没有了  谢谢\n那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.99,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}出了好多汗\n带回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.03,0:02:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}你高潮的时候\n是什么样的声音呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}又是什么表情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}邮件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.80,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}L发来的邮件\n我是L  商量一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.80,0:03:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}现在还未实行轮奸\n感觉很欲求不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}之前说过的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.31,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很想对绘里香实行轮奸\n可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}要轮奸了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好吧  做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好的  做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}但是两个人不够\n再招一个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}执行轮奸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.73,0:04:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}目标是216号\n美人秘书片桐绘里香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}征集一名\n热情有经验的同道中人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}已送信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.89,0:04:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}真的要侵犯片桐绘里香吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}那么一定请让我加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}一直很想侵犯美人秘书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.53,0:04:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}轮奸有你的参加一定很有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.91,0:04:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}感谢参加\n请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}已送信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.55,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}社长秘书美畜同好会\n轮奸目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}片桐绘里香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}决定诱拐的手段了\n趁着她和公司警卫说话的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}下班时职工不适用的楼梯\n在哪里开始狙击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}18点开始执行  拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.16,0:07:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很顺利吧\n果然调查的很得当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.17,0:07:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}美人秘书太棒了  好兴奋啊\n谁  你们是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.92,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}你是不可能和我们抵抗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.43,0:07:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}我简直太兴奋了\n做这种事情有何企图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}安静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.84,0:07:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.11,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}老实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}掰开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}尽情享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}真不听话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}来接吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好软啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}看这里喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}看看里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}混账
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}快来舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}想舔吧\n我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要反抗喔  老实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很容易就进去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}别动喔\n不然我们会更兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.93,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}怎么可能  在侵犯你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}可以插进去吗\n试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.21,0:11:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要动喔  进去试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}湿了喔\n是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}看来她也兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.87,0:12:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}过来吧  用力插\n不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很激动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}手拿开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.67,0:13:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}手拿开喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.57,0:13:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}来插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}老实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}生插喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.98,0:14:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}太爽了  好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.66,0:15:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}被侵犯很爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}尽情插吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好好看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}内射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}可以吧  好兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.75,0:16:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}内射了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}该我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}老实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.43,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}越挣扎越舒服喔\n下面越紧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.45,0:18:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}给我看脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}老实一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.50,0:18:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}让他帮忙口交吧\n是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很想要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}很想要的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.89,0:19:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}后入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}给我看脸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.57,0:20:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}在侵犯你喔  开心一点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}口交吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}刚射过的肉棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}舔干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}下一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}来接吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.28,0:21:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}接吻吧  不是喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}看着我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.56,0:21:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}用力插了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.48,0:22:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好舒服啊  我也内射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.49,0:22:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.27,0:23:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}轮奸才刚刚开始喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.04,0:23:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.74,0:25:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}好的  需要的材料够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.78,0:25:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}检查一下你的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.78,0:25:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.18,0:25:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}有头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.18,0:26:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}日记本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.83,0:26:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}有牙刷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.83,0:26:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}要刷牙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.97,0:26:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.97,0:26:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.60,0:26:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}变态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.60,0:26:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\shad0}继续说啊
